OL,3,CRising homeschooling trends blamed on
OL,4,Cpandemic
OL,6,FThe number of children being
OL,7,Fhomeschooled in Jersey has almost
OL,8,Fdoubled in the past five years.
OL,10,FOfficial figures show that in the 2019-
OL,11,F20 academic year, 41 children were
OL,12,Fbeing educated entirely outside of a
OL,13,Fformal school setting; in the 2024-25
OL,14,Fyear, that figure has risen to a total
OL,15,Fof 81.
OL,17,FIt's thought the steady rise is
OL,18,Frelated to the impact of the Covid-19
OL,19,Fpandemic.
