OL,6,FDuring the 2020-21 academic year, many
OL,7,Fof the island's children were forced
OL,8,Fto learn at home.
OL,10,FThe island's government thinks this
OL,11,Fperiod encouraged parents to engage
OL,12,Fdirectly with their child's learning
OL,13,Fand understand what kinds of support
OL,14,Fand resources are available to them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
