OL,3,CRising homeschooling trends blamed on
OL,4,Cpandemic
OL,6,FThe pandemic also affected youth
OL,7,Fwellbeing, and in a statement
OL,8,Freflecting on the figures, the
OL,9,Fgovernment adds: "We now know the
OL,10,Fimpact of that period of time,
OL,11,Fspecifically on our children and young
OL,12,Fpeople's mental health.
OL,14,F"Subsequently, there has been an
OL,15,Fincrease in the number of children
OL,16,Fbeing educated at home".
OL,18,FSome of the parents choosing to
OL,19,Fhomeschool say a different, less
OL,20,Fpressured environment is a better fit.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
