OL,6,FCameron Elliott says taking his two
OL,7,Fchildren Aria and Noah out of school
OL,8,Ftwo years ago has allowed them to grow
OL,9,Fin their own way.
OL,11,F"They were both coming home quite
OL,12,Fupset for different reasons", he says,
OL,13,F"we tried working with the teachers to
OL,14,Fresolve it and for them to be happy,
OL,15,Fbut I just felt like we didn't get
OL,16,Fanywhere."
