OL,6,FOthers argue that whilst homeschooling
OL,7,Fcan provide a different kind of
OL,8,Fsupport system to those children who
OL,9,Fneed one, it shouldn't be viewed as a
OL,10,Flong-term solution.
OL,12,FMarianne Adams, a former teacher and
OL,13,Fprivate tutor, says "education depends
OL,14,Fon circumstances" and thinks it would
OL,15,Fbe difficult to achieve high academic
OL,16,Fstandards at GCSE or A-level without
OL,17,Fthe support of a school.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
