OL,6,F"That's not to say it can't happen in
OL,7,Fa home setting", she says, "but you
OL,8,Fhave to be very disciplined and keep
OL,9,Fconsistency to have that level of
OL,10,Feducation from home".
OL,12,FShe also fears children being educated
OL,13,Fat home for significant periods of
OL,14,Ftime might miss out on opportunities
OL,15,Ffor social interaction.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
