OL,6,F"Interaction with peers is so
OL,7,Fimportant. If someone is being
OL,8,Fhomeschooled, making sure there's
OL,9,Fbalance and opportunities for social
OL,10,Finteraction - particularly whilst
OL,11,Fthey're young and developing - is very
OL,12,Fimportant", she adds.
OL,14,FParents choosing to homeschool will
OL,15,Freceive home visits from members of
OL,16,Fthe Education Department and
OL,17,Fsafeguarding officers every year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
